# Amaca Design System — Cursor rules

This project uses **Amaca**: dark-first, single typeface (Satoshi), one brand accent (magenta) spent sparingly. Full spec in `DESIGN.md`; full token tables in `tokens.css` / `tokens.dtcg.json`. On conflict, `DESIGN.md` wins.

**Reference every value as a token by name (`var(--token)`). Never hardcode a hex, px, or `cubic-bezier`.** If a value isn't on a scale, stop and ask — never extend the system silently.

**Token roles** (full scales in `tokens.css`): brand `--magenta-500` (#F051D5) = primary/CTA/focus · neutral `--obsidian-950` page → `--obsidian-050` bone, text `--obsidian-100` · supporting (rare) `--secondary-400` cyan / `--tertiary-500` petrol / `--success|warning|danger|info` (feedback only) · type Satoshi `--t-micro 10 … --t-body 15 … --t-h1 76` (one H1/page) · spacing 4px grid `--s-1 4 … --s-32 128` · radius `--r-md 8` / `--r-lg 12` · motion 6 durations + 4 easings (`--ease-decel` signature), always with a `prefers-reduced-motion` fallback.

**Laws:** 85/10/5 (≤5% magenta, one CTA per viewport) · off-scale values break precision (`padding:14px` ✗ → `var(--s-3) var(--s-4)` ✓) · motion is feedback, not decoration.

**Components:** reuse canonical classes (`.btn-primary` once per screen, `.card`, `.field`, `.select`…); a new `.classname` not in the canonical set is a gap → surface it, never ship a silent variant.

**A11y floor:** color never alone (+ shape + label) · no text < 12px / body < 14px · persistent labels (placeholder ≠ label) · `alt` on images · focus follows reading order, dual-ring on pressables · no auto-advance · touch 44×44. On `--magenta-500` use a dark label (`--obsidian-950`, AA); the one ratified exception is `.btn-primary` (light label, scoped to that CTA).

**Conventions:** semantic HTML first — `<button>`/`<a>`, never `<div onclick>`; `kebab-case` files; no AI tells in copy ("delve", "leverage", "robust", "seamless", "effortlessly"). **Never ship:** gradient card backgrounds · emoji in UI · drop shadows for emphasis · radius > 16px on small components · filled/multi-color icons · carousels / auto-advance · centered body text > 80ch · placeholder-as-label · magenta > 5% of viewport · a `cubic-bezier` literal or `font-size:14px` in component CSS · a token value hand-copied into JS.

```css
.btn-primary{ background:var(--magenta-500); color:var(--obsidian-050);
  padding:var(--s-3) var(--s-5); border-radius:var(--r-md);
  font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:var(--t-body); font-weight:500;
  transition:background var(--d-quick) var(--ease-standard); }
.btn-primary:focus-visible{ outline:2px solid var(--obsidian-100); outline-offset:3px;
  box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(240,81,213,0.35); }
```

**Verify before shipping:** zero hardcoded hex/px/`cubic-bezier` in component code (grep or a token-aware stylelint) · 85/10/5 holds · a11y floor passes · every transition has a `prefers-reduced-motion` fallback. (Add your project's own build/test/lint alongside.)
